10. Risk Assessment and Mitigation

10.1 Technical Risks

Quantum Hardware Failure:

· Risk: Quantum decoherence or hardware failure
· Mitigation: Redundant quantum systems, classical fallback
· Probability: Low (0.1% annually)
· Impact: Medium (temporary service degradation)

Consciousness Interface Risks:

· Risk: Unauthorized consciousness access
· Mitigation: Multi-factor consciousness authentication
· Probability: Very Low (0.01% annually)
· Impact: High (privacy breach)

AI Alignment Risks:

· Risk: AI developing unintended behaviors
· Mitigation: Trinity Council oversight, ethical constraints
· Probability: Low (0.1% annually)
· Impact: Critical (system compromise)

